item.title: CVE-2017-0305|2024-08-05T13:03:56.813Z -- f5%20networks -- ssl%20intercept%20iapp%20version
item.description: F5 SSL Intercept iApp version 1.5.0 - 1.5.7 is vulnerable to an unauthenticated, remote attack that may allow modification of the BIG-IP system configuration, extraction of sensitive system files, and possible remote command execution on the system when deployed using the Explicit Proxy feature plus SNAT Auto Map option for egress traffic.
